company_name: KARL HINRICH REIMER INH. KLAUS-HINRICH REIMER BLUMENBINDEREI UND FRIEDH.
information: The company KARL HINRICH REIMER INH. KLAUS-HINRICH REIMER BLUMENBINDEREI UND FRIEDH., is a Wholesaler, founded in 1981, which operates in the Indoor and greenhouse plants, floristry industry. It is based in Flensburg, Germany.
